{"tid":1737580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係「有gear既上前」係「上前既人確保齊gear」","createTime":"2019-11-19T03:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T16:31:46.000Z","uid":36716,"like":266,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"6f7d4380942274e20a9e43bc472e82163b1fbf3e","tid":1737580,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:57:33.000Z","msg":"強迫有gear既即刻上前<br />\n只會令<br />\n<br />\n嘗試戴gear既手足有心理壓力，令人卻步<br />\n<br />\n永遠一步一步黎，今日係前面返黎<br />\n見到無gear既係咁叫有gear既上前<br />\n<br />\n如果真係想幫前面<br />\n應該係講<br />\n<br />\n「我上前，有無人肯比gear我」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>唔好諗到帶左豬咀就要上前</strong></span>，帶豬咀為咗防毒氣 最理想係每個人都帶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n帶豬咀唔上前亦絕對無問題，因為豬咀係防禦工具，其實係應該每個人都有，同和唔和理非無關"},{"pid":"924f9991ec21a7f157fde67ce2cc58c575d71b45","tid":1737580,"uid":50194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:59:10.000Z","msg":"幫你推 btw 依家hktvmall仲有無得買"},{"pid":"50b097e26754f85a327238671c056cdb9cc08fc1","tid":1737580,"uid":36716,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:59:28.000Z","msg":"我真係相信有好多人唔帶豬咀係驚比人覺得係勇武<br />\n有企前責任<br />\n<br />\n但並唔係，前線帶豬咀都只係防禦措施，同上唔上無關，你返工都可以帶"},{"pid":"b2ac6f6007fb3c75ccff186581fe1d42c848977e","tid":1737580,"uid":36716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"924f9991ec21a7f157fde67ce2cc58c575d71b45","tid":1737580,"uid":50194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:59:10.000Z","msg":"幫你推 btw 依家hktvmall仲有無得買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:00:01.000Z","msg":"好似話賣哂，好似暫時真係要五金舖先買到"},{"pid":"f5e9694564c5491f9a98a276aa079b6e1672f70e","tid":1737580,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:11:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04e0f2f9a42b88735c006d04d10857fd58e501eb","tid":1737580,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:11:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8ebf7762f5c7e08b98de659f10a9260eacbcb8c8","tid":1737580,"uid":151313,"like":6,"d